description: Aspose.Imaging Image Merge Micro Application allows to add image merge feature to you .NET application or just use it via command line.
summary: Aspose.Imaging Image Merge Micro Application allows collage creation from several input images in the desired image format. You may customize output using various layouts, adjustments of input images, setting margins size, and background color. It seamlessly enhances your own .NET, C#, VB.NET, and ASP.NET applications to merge images and photos, or you may use it via the command line without coding. Aspose.Imaging Image Marge Micro Application works on any.NET7 compatible OS (Windows, Linux, macOS).
title: Aspose.Imaging Image Merge Micro Application for .NET
